OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fquite cloudy with scattered showers in
OL,7,Fthe evening. Generally becoming drier
OL,8,Fthrough the night but still a few
OL,9,Fshowers around. Windy around the
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FCloudy and windy with rain
OL,13,Fthrough the morning, heavy at times.
OL,14,FBecoming dry but still cloudy in the
OL,15,Fearly afternoon, before bright spells
OL,16,Fdevelop later with the odd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
