OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith some rain Friday morning,
OL,7,Fbrighter with the odd shower later.
OL,8,FDry start Saturday before further rain
OL,9,Fspreading later. Cloudy and breezy
OL,10,Fwith outbreaks of rain on Sunday.
